54
00:02:45,471 --> 00:02:47,932
So you have some walking, some flying, and some swimming.

55
00:02:48,592 --> 00:02:51,753
You have line-of-sight awareness, omni-awareness, and audio awareness.

56
00:02:52,373 --> 00:02:55,814
And you have ranged combat, melee combat, and area-of-effect attacks.

57
00:02:56,774 --> 00:02:58,215
And then you can combine these, right?

58
00:02:59,075 --> 00:03:04,577
You can say, okay, I want to create a bot that is flying, that has line-of-sight awareness,

59
00:03:04,917 --> 00:03:06,577
and has an area-of-effect attack.

60
00:03:07,377 --> 00:03:08,998
