113
00:06:05,468 --> 00:06:10,570
And basically what he did is he took two groups, one of them were looking at kitchen sink objects

114
00:06:11,211 --> 00:06:17,034
and the other group was looking at emotional arousing things like dangerous animals or

115
00:06:17,934 --> 00:06:20,535
crashes, mutilated bodies, stuff like that.

116
00:06:21,156 --> 00:06:24,337
And then he asked afterwards, how many of these pictures do you recall?

117
00:06:24,637 --> 00:06:26,418
